{"tid":1299955,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"與其努力送孩子入讀名校，不如努力送孩子讀國際學校","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:17:00.000Z","uid":81028,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"70baa45bcd543c6ca5fe91485d3a958b6b650233","tid":1299955,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"大家不時在電視或新聞報道看到很多家長為自己的仔女在升中放榜入到名校喜極而泣。<br />\n落榜的孩子，哭的不是他們的仔女，而是家長們。<br />\n說到底，不就是一群<strong>窮中產</strong>，拼命想送仔女到一些性價比高一些的學校。<br />\n<br />\n國際學校，從來不能用性價比來衡量，是一種文化。入讀的仔女不用接受香港的中式教育，課程直接選用外國優良的教育系統，仔女在裡面出來後，受到氛圍，將來是社會名流紳士和淑女。<br />\n<br />\n如果你準備將來生小孩，請努力送孩子讀國際學校吧，這才是送他們最好的一份禮物。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=irJMcFTGI8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DirJMcFTGI8E&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1d3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=010adfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=irJMcFTGI8E</a>"},{"pid":"6be67b0d4c86b0203ee0c7ac799f191f01caf741","tid":1299955,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"...國際學校 學殘體字喎"},{"pid":"a8373724ddc69971c9873614dbefb83141d7ad5f","tid":1299955,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"送出外國最好"},{"pid":"6dc6aa557f7df8d20740f7bad9312559eaf672e0","tid":1299955,"uid":29238,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"最TOP果d國際學校就係<br />\n其他果d就算9數啦  入到去成班蝗  學普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c08e65d14fc60d85a63b52a46ac8decbfc8dcb8","tid":1299955,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"讀國際學校, 識下唔同地方人, 真係要出國都多個門路"},{"pid":"385bc58d4f2c444e8459070f5af7eab0f43e3a15","tid":1299955,"uid":110222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"大陸嘅國際學校規定咗外國人先可以讀<br />\n第時